content.detailedDescription: At 4am i woke and couldn't get back to sleep. frustrated i looked out my window to the east and noticed a bright light. i decided to get dressed and go look closer. using my star app it seems i saw jupiter or mars. then i decided to look at the moon and watch the stars since i was already outside, hoping it would make me tired. the temperature was 27degrees, a bit chilly with a slight wind coming from the east. i stood behind my garden shed to block the breeze and then decided to play with my phone camera and photograph the moon, since it was so clear out. only a few high thin clouds. i propped my phone up on a post and took multiple photos. upon reviewing them i noticed a blue round light near the moon which appears to have moved from above the moon to the right hand side then it blurs out. all the photos were taken within seconds of each other. not sure what it was but neat anyhow.
content.summary: Woke up noticed a bright light went outside to look

content.detailedDescription: Went out side to lock cars door at about 9pm, when i saw 3 bright orbs in the sky ,hovering  then diving in to portage bay. i watched them hover for about 15 mins  before they dove in to the bay. scared  the hell out of me.
content.summary: 3 glowing orbs diving in to portage bay

content.detailedDescription: I reached meditative state for only the 4th time, i was in deep meditation, and attempting to invite and vector in et's. i had the feeling they were coming from alaska. i awakened and went outside and looked nw towards alaska. i saw what i thought were ufos, off in that direction, as you can here me say in the video. however i realized quickly they were white birds flying in a circular pattern, and the sun was reflecting off of them, making it look like they were shinning and disappearing when they turned. regardless i filmed for a bit, i could not figure out what kind of birds they were. at the end of the video, i look up because a bird flew right over my head. i only filmed for 1 minute. nothing seemed to happen.  later that night i went to show my mom the birds. curious as to what kind that were. so i watch the film, to my surprise i see no birds at all!!??!! for the entire minute you see no birds ?! not even the one that flew 15 feet over me head at the end of the clip. but if you look closely from 10-14 seconds you will see an orb appear on the right side of the screen above the tree.  then it makes some weird movements in front of the tree,  and shoots downward off the camera. also another orb is seen near the very end of the video, at the bottom of the screen, it seems to be accelerating away from the camera.?! what a strange first contact!! i believe an entity edited the birds oitvif my video, then appeared to say hi, and confirm his actions. it's not overwhelming. but the facts are quite interesting, and life changing to me.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Ce-5 encounter. with video.

content.detailedDescription: Was outside at 11 pm. saw what i thought was a life flight helicopter because urgent care very close to where i live. thought i would watch it land so stayed outside. object stopped and just hovered. watched for few moments then decided to get my camera. took 4 or 5 pictures. object was horizontal cylinder shaped with different colors. also got couple od pictures of same object but ball shaprd. have seen objects here 2 or 3 times.
content.summary: Thought it was helicopter until it stopped and hovered

content.detailedDescription: I was at work in mid-city los angeles when a fellow co-worker told me to go up to the roof to see some unidentified objects high up in the bright sky. it was approximately 4 pm and i joined the rest on the building's roof and saw 3-4 bright orbs in a near row traveling from east to north, then change direction from east to west. these lights were very high up, changing from white to bright red, seemingly pulsating. even though it was so far away it was very bright in the clear blue sky. the sky was clear and some of the objects seem to appear and then disappear. the objects were moving very slowly, it was defiantly not airplanes or helicopters. the original employee said he saw 6 of these orbs but when i got to the roof i only saw 3. fifteen minutes later they disappeared. i took some video but my video does no justice to what we saw because i had no tripod nearby and it looks like a tiny white dot in the blue sky. the object was also pulsating bright red (crimson) and that did not come out in the video. interestingly my co-worker's cell phone was malfunctioning, but my sony hd video camera was working fine.
content.summary: 3-6 orbs changing color from white to red. pulsating.Multiple witnesses.

content.detailedDescription:
It was 3:30 am and i was driving home from my public safety position at depauw university.  i observed an orb in the western sky,  it initially appeared to be a harvest moon setting in the west.  it was not.

what drew my total attention was the enormous size of the orb.  it was immediately obvious it was not the moon.

it appeared 50 to 100 times the size of the normal moon size.  it was fiery orange in color and brilliant in contrast to the black sky with spotty cumulus clouds, (view able from the glow of the orb as white fluffy clouds).

it moved slightly north and south before dropping beyond the horizon in a due west direction.  it initially appeared at about 30 degrees above the western horizon.

i was shocked to see it disappear so quickly from sight considering the size and seemingly stagnate motion.  i would estimate the distance from earth to be fairly close as in possible flight levels around 35 to 40,000 feet.

i can not stress enough how big it was and how quickly it really moved while appearing to be motionless.  i was in total awe.  i drove from in 231 to 1000 s as fast as possible and drove west on 1000 s until it disappeared over the horizon, approximately 4,5 miles a total viewing period of 5 to 7 minutes.

note:

i have noticed several several instances of space junk re-entry prior to this viewing.  they had shape and were blue, green and brilliant white light falling from north to south. coincidence i don't know??  no time to take pictures.
content.summary: One orb at least 50 times the size of teh moon blinding orange brilliant light setting as sun would due west lasted 5 minutes unbelievable x 1000

content.detailedDescription:
I had stopped at my moms house to bring her the mail.  as i was about to leave, i saw through her front window an extremely bright white light moving through the trees.  we went out onto the front porch to get a better look and saw that it was slowly moving east from the northwest at about the tree top level.  directly below it was another intensely bright white light that followed the first ones movements precisely.   

looking up, we saw two flashing objects that would silently hover for a bit then bob and weave or zigzag occasionally.  they flashed what appeared to be a random pattern of red, blue, white, yellow, and a greenish yellow.  after a few minutes of watching we heard the sounds of helicopters approaching from the south.  the white lights in the trees went out like the flipping of a switch.  after maybe ten more seconds, the other two objects shot straight up until we couldn't see them anymore.  

the two helicopters flew over and appeared to make a couple of very wide circles around the area then flew away to the south east.

altogether it may have taken five or six minutes from the time we first saw the white lights to the time the helicopters flew away.  i tried to take pictures but the camera died after only taking four.  and only one of them show anything.
content.summary: I observed two white lights moving through the trees and two multicolored blinking lights in the sky shortly followed by helicopters.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving home from a meeting down fallen timber road in elizabeth, pennsylvania when i noticed this bright green light in my view. it fell from the sky, but i lost sight of it behind a house. it looked like a large star, but shined like a "glow stick green" in color. it fell what seemed to be straight down out of the sky and not like a shooting star shoots across the sky. it did not leave any type of trail in the sky. i was unsure of what it could be and was confused and anxious, but completely aware. i immediately came home and looked on the computer to try and find out what it could be.
content.summary: A large, bright, green ball of light that fell quickly. like a falling star.

content.detailedDescription: i witness a couple of ufo sightings, the first sighting in approx. 2002, on top of the river hillside of the allegheny river, i saw two pink colored beams around 6:30am that were equal distance in width smooth sides from the cloudy foggy sky that stretched from high above to the river���i made a witness stand with me and ponder..This rare phenomena the width as wide as a silo and the space was equal distance the space was equal in between���.It was two perfect columns���.; the second phenomena, was fall of 2005, i came outside with my children and photograph over 200 dragonflies on my front porch in pittsburgh, this was a one time in a life time event, too���the third and the event that may help me understand in ufo theories���i witness in may 2012 and reported this ufo sighting to the weather channel: high powered fast moving sparkling lit objects, six in number, straight-on flying and s- shaped movement of some of the vehicles, 3 sets of two ���tangerine��� lit air ufo���s from my home over the allegheny river, @ 2:30 in the morning during a stormy cloudy evening where the horizon and white part clearing in the sky gave a clear observation as heavy bluish dark clouds laid above the clearing , could of these been drones.?..Nothing in my textbook of studied ever could explain this phenomena���family members are pilots, my father was a pilot and international traveler, and lived near the marine corps air station so i do know what airplanes, f18, jets, helicopter headlights look like, too. ok hope this documents something of relevance. also spring of 2015 witness a massive no noise triangular ufo with only 6 round light dim pale yellow it was close enough to see the screens ; spring of 2015 red light linger in the air.. bright and very unusual movements; also finally, as i was star gazing.. saw a ufo erratically move from on spot to another, most definitely a ufo !I was at my home as an observer for all events except the first sighting. movement of light from objects, so out-of-this world most definitely space oriented crafts. ok lastly i saw drops of visible long drops of gold that left circle marks on my driveway too...About many > than 10 gold paint colored drops on me and in front of my walking path i really was a little bewildered by this and reported this and painted a portrait of me and all the un-identified items listed here that i saw as a witness. peace out !
content.summary: All my awareness of seeing ufo was real and i was responsible enough to report this evidence to help aeronautical concerns.!

content.detailedDescription: I live on long island,just down the road from brookhaven labs.. i see a lot of strange objects at lest 4 to 5 times a month and will often use my ultraviolet. light to try and signal whatever they are. on t he night of november 23,2015 at 6:45pm eastern time. i observed two bright white lights with no sound and cigar shaped moving east northeast with no sound. then i watched it move higher in elevation then just stop. i watched it for little over an hour. then i could see 4 to 5 other craft in a circle formation around the larger cigar shape craft. not the first time seeing these things but it was the first time that i saw the cigar shape craft so close. i think the reason i see so many ufo here is because of brookhaven labs and the tests that they do there. i can tell you that until you see it,you just might doubt it,but here over long island i see a lot of strange ufos.Even as i write this the cigar shape object is still out there. i don't have anyway of capturing these objects,well,because im poor.
content.summary: On back deck  saw a black cigar shape craft with two huge lights on each end but were engines not lights fly over house no sound then ascended to a point then just stopped. then i saw4 to 5 other craft in a huge circlee pattern.

content.detailedDescription: I was traveling westbound on bee caves road (2244), when i noticed a vertical trail in the sky. i thought this one was a bit odd, as it was vertical - straight up and down with no visible object leading it. i do understand light refraction works and that often what we think we see is most times just our eyes playing tricks on us, but something about this  just seemed weird. i continued to glance at the vertical trail as i drove, and then noticed as i got closer to my destination that there was now an object that was moving horizontally across the sky, with the trail coming out behind it. i realized that it would pass me if i didn't park soon and get a picture, so i pulled over and zoomed in as much as my camera would allow. i took 4 rapid fire pictures with my iphone, and actually stopped taking pictures as it passed over me, and got back in my car because i got a very uneasy feeling. while i was taking the pictures, i was looking directly at the object (not through the phone) and i swear it was changing shapes as it moved across the sky. if i hadn't seen the trail, and the sun hadn't been setting, i don't know that i would have even seen the object, i feel like the sun's light was affecting its perceivable "shape". i got back in my car and proceeded down a driveway, got back out the car and (literally) 20 seconds later, it was gone. the trail was gone. there was no trace of it in the sky. what i saw looked like a small pink/red/orange orb that appeared to morph as it moved from a clam shape, to a cylinder to an oval. pictures included are labeled in the order they were taken.
content.summary: Strange orb spotted in sky on my way home from work

content.detailedDescription:
I was in the street waiting for a bus, near to a place when hours before took place a fire that burns 10 or more houses.

i was a soft raining but with visibility. i note the object, it looked like a big petroleum drop, floating in the air,  changing shape. i call a person near to confirm i was not crazy, and both stay to walk to the object, that was quiet over the ruins of the fire. then the object start to move and increasing speed it disappear.
content.summary: It was like a big oil drop on the sky hours after a fire was consuming the populated area

content.detailedDescription:
Approx 9:00 pm or 21:00 hours. clear evening, no clouds, temps in the mid 30's. went out to have a smoke and noticed a movement to my right peripheral side vision in the star filled sky.  saw what appeared as a fuzzy outline of a v formation or triangle craft directly above. hard to discern it as it appeared slightly lighter then the dark background sky, fuzzy edges with a translucent appearance. very difficult to see unless looking right at it. no lights, no sound and its glide path was to the south se. watched it for 5-6 seconds before it faded from view. speed looked like around 200 mph at say 3000 feet altitude, just a guess thou as i could not tell it's size.  when first overhead it would have been the size of my hand at arms length. object did not reflect from the moon that evening and for a lack of better words, appeared to cloak it's self somehow to the background. very strange.  i had my cell phone out however there was not enough time to capture it as i was wondering what it was in the first place. i am knowledgeable in earth sciences,known aircraft and consider myself an amateur astronomer. it matched the dark sky so much, i doubt a photo would have shown it unless during the day.  again this object flew silently down/above main street in a city of 40,000 + citizens and no one else saw it?    
another ufo sighting page shows the same object about 20 minutes before in the community of ames,approx 70 miles away on the same evening.  this at least gives my report a little more substance.  thank you.
content.summary: Triangle shaped object which flew silently above in a straight line, appeared to nearly match the dark clear sky

content.detailedDescription:
The morning of november 13th at 5am my partner noticed an unusual light in the sky and he woke me up to see it. we have a cell tower, but it was not the cell tower light. it was in the south eastern sky. he got out of bed, put a robe on to go outside and have a better look. he came back in to get my cell phone to take a photo. when he went back out, it was gone. he reported to me that it looked like it had moved in the sky from where he first observed it but that he did not see it move. it appeared to him to be like many very white stars that were clustered together in a round shape that was larger than a planet.
the morning of november 23rd, i woke up at 5:30am and saw the same light in the same portion of the sky. i got right up, put on a robe and went outside to take a look. then i went back inside to tell my partner and get my cell phone to take a photo. when i came out it was still there. to get a better view (some bare winter trees branches obstructed a clear view) i walked approximately 100 feet past our trees to our field. it looked bigger than a planet in the sky and the lights appeared to be in a triangular shape. it was not moving and looked high enough to be an airplane.
i took a photo with my cell phone. i cropped the photo to try to get a closer look.
content.summary: Saw large

content.detailedDescription: I was home on my back deck drawing some art with the deck lights on, i felt odd (6th sense kinda thing) and looked up. there was a roughly 20-30 foot saucer less than 6 feet above my head. it had 4 glowing white panels and 4 lights on it as well. the lights were a golden orange. i am a repeat abductee and i knew exactly what it was when i saw it. before i was drawing i was star watching with my binoculars, so i had them with me. as soon as i saw the saucer i began cursing and screaming for my mother. the object seemed to notice that and silently flew toward pikes peak. my mother came out and was upset that i was loud. i told her to look at the object with my binoculars. she just glanced in the general area and said its just pikes peak. i took one last look and saw the object (north of the peak and near the tree line in altitude) and it flew over the peak and used the mountain as cover to get away. my mother grabbed me and brought me inside. it was not long after that my hair started to recede and im only 19 years old. i felt surprised and aggressive and a little disappointed and angry that my mother did not see it nor did she really care. ive been dealing with ufos and entities since i was 17. there are many other events just like this i can report.
content.summary: Was out on my deck and saw a ufo less than 6 feet above my head.

content.detailedDescription: Cell phone footage from back porch november 16 2015 at 3:30 am..The light at bottom is the neighbor outside light pole half block away. that is me zooming in and out and panning the area. you will see neighborhood lights for reference points. what made me look outside was an overwhelming sense to look. i was fixing a snack for myself because i had insomnia. i put the food in microwave and looked out the back door window. noticed the pulsating colors immediately went and put on shoes and jacket grabbed cell phone. set the camera to video and stepped out onto the deck and to my amazement i was able to see it..Starting the video and referenced the neighbors street light pole. began recording and tried to pan around and see if i was able to pick up stars or anything else. the lights other than the pulsating one are all from neighbors homes and street lights. went in after 3 minutes or so microwave was beeping..Ate snack, decided to look out again and it had moved to a different location from left side of light to right side. i had noticed a second red light, and a tiny white light. i tried to capture the red light to the left of the object and barely could see it on the camera. then returned to the original object and it slowly moved behind a branch. i refocused on it and it suddenly was no longer there. this was an extremely exciting capture as i have noticed either the same object or similar one in the same vicinity of my neighborhood,but was unable to capture it. i am not sure what this is, but suspect that i have captured a ufo on video.
content.summary: Cell phone footage from back porch november 16 2015 at 3:30 am..The light at bottom is the neighbor outside light pole half block away. that is me zooming in and out and panning the area. you will see neighborhood lights for reference points.

content.detailedDescription:
Walked outside after 9pm facing due east i noticed the airplanes were not in their normal flight paths "in fact" abnormal . i saw 2 small blinking lights flying in tandem one in front of the other like they were attached by a string ? i though they were helicopters until they flew directly over me, completely silent . they continued to do a circling pattern my best guess is a mile radius then passing over our place directly over where i was standing. the 2 main objects  were again flying in tandem sometimes close sometimes far away , i also noticed other small lights flying around? the 2 being observed at one point a third appeared and all three blinked red in a triangle pattern as the 2 passed under the third the third dropped down to the one tailing the first and stopped...... the 2 continued over me and continued the circular pattern. i am a professional videographer ive spent countless ours filming helicopters, planes small air craft for prestigious companies i am familiar with flight characteristics and these flew nothing like them. now drones? i can see how these things could have been drones but for there size numbers and the amount of time they spent in the air i can not deduce? and why over a residential area? with this said i recorded them on a hpx 500 with a 8 to 120 fujinon lens with a 2x extender at 12 db on a tripod, my goal was to get the best footage to see what they were. my feelings? well altho i would love proof we are not alone in this universe i watched and filmed these things for 45 min with a critical eye i shot the planes as well for comparison, i did tell close friends about this and they said they read about it in the paper or news and it was a military exercise with helicopters,or drones???
ok..... my conclusion.
if? it was military maneuvers over 16th st and glendale a residential area with super secret drones for over an hour? i have the most "rock solid" footage i have ever seen of these craft.

if? it was et? i have the most "rock solid" footage i have ever seen of ufos over a residential area. 

i lost sight of them over my building towards the south east.
content.summary: 4-5 lights ( 2 circling )observed and filmed for 45 mins

content.detailedDescription:
I was at a friend's to visit and i was coming back to my house, i went in and came back out to walk my dog. i started to walk my dog and my dog stopped and was looking up in the air.
i also looked up in the air and there was two lights coming about 20ft to 30ft away from me and the dog.
i was thinking that this is stars but i was wrong as the lights got closer
it was a black cigar shape object as i moved back to see where it was going over top of my house it just vanish in the air.
but i can tell you that it was as black as black but it was solid.
it was flying over electric lines for our lights in the neighborhood.
content.summary: Cigar shape' black one light in front one light in back no noise.

content.detailedDescription:
I was walking my two dogs around our area, looked at the sky to see some stars w/c i didn't find, then noticed something moving from up above. i followed it with my eyes because i was curious whether if it was a plane / bird / a drone. however, as i proceeded following it with my eyes, i saw a strange pyramid shaped with patterns on it, no lights nor sounds. it was flying smoothly & quickly. after it got out of my sight, i saw two military helicopters together flying towards my location. after a few seconds, they split up. the other went to the right & the other took the path to the left. it seems like they are trying to search for something / someone? 

i'm was amazed & kind of still doubting about it. so i contacted my fiance & informed him everything i saw. i even posted it on my facebook & instragram accounts. i don't care if no one believes me. i know i witnessed something foreign from this world.
content.summary: Flying smoothly, pyramid shaped with patterns

content.detailedDescription: Using my telescope to view the moon. (type of scope everything is upside down and backwards). object enters field of view on telescope. scope is 400 mm focal length with 3.6 mm lens = 111x magnification. object moved very quickly less than 1 second out of scope view. could be a satellite? but it left a trail that lasted very shortly black to white to nothing. checked my astronomy software, no comets or asteroids in vicinity. last satellite to pass would have been 9 to 10 minutes prior to observation. had my telescope hooked to my cell phone which caught the video. phone dates the video november 14th, 6:38 pm. i have extracted the small section of the video, but still retain the original if needed for further purposes. would just like to know what i captured on video.
content.summary: Light streak with trail

content.detailedDescription:
In dc met with some friends and met this individual stan c petrov (they call him the inventor and he is the cto of company called inovatzia -not a secret ).
at first i didn't notice anything unusual however after shaking his hand it felt cold as ice yet he didn't appear in any distress, than we sat on the table and ordered food (he didn't eat any of it ?! not a single bite ).
as he was telling a story about the ancient thracians and their believes in immortality he got a phone call (his phone lid up, looked like apple but was light and had bit of gas or steam coming out of it). he said they "invent things" i asked him can i see it and he let me play with it -this thing was the lightest (iphone like phone) - felt light and  looked like it was made of gold/silver metal or metal  like material?! he told me that he is "testing all sorts of materials " well i can say that - 
this material  was nothing like what i have ever seen or felt  - the shine, and texture simply nothing to compare it with. 
next he showed some photos and videos to my friend. i also looked into the screen - incredible photos and videos  of all sorts of microscopic organisms living on people however the colors details and resolution was nothing i have ever seen. 
further more there was photos and videos of all sorts of medical machines in various "trials" that truly looked like star trek sort of technology.
at some point my friend's battery died and stan pulled out a what appeared to be tiny rectangular thing with blue and red light coming out of it in pulses ? "reactor of some sort?" in about 4-5 min my friend's iphone 5s went from dead to 40% - than stan talked about that "too much ampers we don't want to fry your battery"  this device was not like a battery, but looked like mini radiator and as it started charging its surface  got sort of wet and than icy.

afterwatds me and my friend went to my house there my friend shared with me that stan has likely saved his  life "i was really sick stan was introduced to me by a friend." "  i got his contact info  and met him."
"after listening to me he said that he can't help me since he is simply a medical student. he was really nice and knowledgable as well as supportive. i befriended him .... at some point
he talked about some thing making some sort of serum....  " 
my friend further shared that "im not proud of this but i borrowed some .... without him knowing  and i swear i believe  it helped" ,  he also shared that stan's physical appearance has not changed at all for years ?! " i knew him for over .. years he hasn't changed physically at all and he never sleeps always works making toys!". 
he showed me photos with stan together for over xx  years ago !!! and as far as i could tell he had not changed at all in fact at the restaurant  he was wearing the same jaket and shoes !
for real?! 
finally during our meeting as stan was describing his "dream world" or actually stan's reality - time just lapsed - we had been at the restaurant for over few hours, but i swear it felt like 10-15 minutes.
also my iphone and smart watch had both shut down ?! 
i know my report may sound crazy, but i'm simply expressing what i saw and felt.
i'm not the type of person that believes in extra terrestrial life forms, however stan is either superhuman  or not from this planet.
after this encounter and based on what i saw "the toys" i will seriously concider the possibility of alien life forms or superhumans. 
i called my friend yesterday to express this possibility and he thinks i'm paranoid - lol
"stan is eccentric  inventor that's all if he is hiding things why would he allow  his patents to be public?"
well i looked through his patents using the google search engine and guess what, none of the things i saw were mentioned in the patents i saw.

so do aliens or super humans exist ? stan is one of them.
don't know hope this report is useful to somebody.
content.summary: Alien or superhuman - his name is stan c petrov - using serum affecting  aging, have new type of phones and power sources.

content.altitude: Over 500 Feet (under cloudcover), Over 500 Feet (no cloudcover)

content.detailedDescription: oddly enough, shortly after reporting this event (first time i ever did though i seen objects, triangles possibly tr3b  but never was compelled to report it. next day my laptop just died. i'm borrowing my old mans right now. if i only had aq camera that shot well in the dark. to this day i still see them often but never as many as i did then, i finally got the few pics off my card of the day time siting. this is was sept. the sky looked really unusual so i looked up often (artist, i take interest in beauty and see things most do not. eye for detail. i had a crappy cam a friend gave to me. looking up i noticed huge fire like large "con" trail emerge. like 5 of them with space inbetween (so yeah, not a contrail) then i seen a ball of white light sitting atthe end of the last trail. stationary. it was maybe 7 or 8 at night, sun was just going down, i grabbed the camera to film it. no space. ahhhh. so in a rush i deleted a few photos and was able to snap a few. what they don't capture is some amazing event. not far from the ufo i seen 3 small orange orbs blink on. they started colecting moisture or something basically making a cloud to camo the , i assume, broken ufo. then another very bright white object was approaching from the west. met up for not even a second, combined and off it shot.
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering,Other
content.summary: I posted a report about numerous star craft  during venus mars, jupiter line up.

content.detailedDescription:
my husband took my cat for a ride to his office at around 2100. the cat had never been in a vehicle before. needless to say when they got to his office the cat jumped out and was lost. my husband did not tell me about this until around  midnight after i had become upset that i could not find the cat. following the typical marital discussion of what a stupid thing i felt that was to do, we both got in my husband's truck and went the 3.5 miles to his office. the temperature had dropped to 28 degrees fahrenheit and i was vey worried for the cat.
     during the next  thirty minutes or so, i placed food, water and boxes outside for the cat in case we could not find him. i called friends who offered to come and join the hunt. they  are night people , one of whom had just left our house around 2200. 
        after speaking with our friends on my cell i stepped back outside in the rear parking lot of the office. i was calling the cat and whistling for him. he is whistle trained. i opened the electric gate to the front parking lot and driveway to check for the cat in the front of the grounds. the fence gate opened by a push of the electric button effortlessly and i stepped across the gate threshold.
        all of a sudden i noticed a group of bright green lights in the sky. as a flight attendant, i know that there is no craft that is covered in all green lights during night flight. the moon was almost full and the sky was clear except for these lights which were just hovering above the road in front of me. i stopped calling my cat and begin walking toward the lights to see what it was. just as suddenly as they appeared they took off in a southern direction so fast that the lights all blurred into what appeared to be one long green light with a descending tail. 
    the lights were so bright and odd. i ran to follow and hoped to see what it was that could do that but it was gone, just gone. the automatic fence then closed and locked me out. i called my hubby on his cell and he had to come outside to let me in because the combination on the electric fence would not allow the it to open.This was odd. 
    i told my hubby what i saw and he suggested we go home. i wasn't scared just confused. i always thought it might scare me if i saw a ufo, but it really didn't . it made me a tad nervous,but more than anything i was worried about the cat. 
      my friends showed up just after we drove off and called them. the cat was hiding under a tree and eagerly ran to the couple and sat in the lady's lap all the way home. i told my friends and she mentioned that green lights had been recently sited in our area.
content.summary: Sudden green lights appeared above the road, stopped tn ok off rapidly

content.detailedDescription: I was picking my husband up from work he was doing on an ongoing remodel in santa ana hill/tustin area and the view was amazing, so i got out of the car to take a few shots of the early sunset over orange county. didn't notice this until later. but i have to say that a lot of strange things have been going on in our skies and otherwise since at least jan. 2015, which is when i started taking notice.
content.summary: Taking pictures of view, didn't notice ufo until looking at photos later.

content.detailedDescription:
My husband and i were heading home from my parents during halftime of the vikings game when out my window, to the south west, i noticed some strangely bright lights. i pointed them out to him by saying, "see, look, i told you there have been weird things in the sky lately!" i figured he would write off the objects but didnt,instead he told me to get some pictures for him because he didn't know what he was seeing. as i tried to get pictures he pulled off the road for me. i took a regular sun set photo and then turned the lighting down so there was no oranges or reds. they stayed still it seemed, but were far enough away it was hard to tell. we could tell based on the landscape whatever they were, they were big. we headed homemail and i tried to keep my eyes on them, they seemed to fade into the orange of the sunset, like, the coloring was so closely the same it was hard to see until i eventually lost them. 

we were traveling south, off 626th ave, taking highway 30 west until county road 14, and could see them clearly from all angles for approximately 15 minutes.
content.summary: We saw bright lights that appeared stationary before fading out

content.detailedDescription: Was resting in upstairs bedroom and looking out window at pretty sky when noticed a silvery white oval object moving from right to left about 10 degrees over horizen. size seemed to be like an aspirin. appeared to be many miles away. object vanished after a few seconds. over next 5 or 6 minutes saw about a dozen more of the same, appearing every 20 seconds or so and vanishing within 3 or 4 seconds. at one point 2 appeared at the same time and seemed to be flying in formation. the one object that was different from the rest remained visable 8 or 9 seconds, traveling straight and emitting changing colors, from red to green to blue before in vanishing. my initial reaction was that this was some kind of space junk entering the atmosphere, but each object seemed to have the same clearly defined shape and all objects seemed to be deliberately heading in the same direction. they did not appear to exhibit the higher speeds associated with meteors or man made debris burning up into he atmosphere. my reaction was that these objects were very beautiful and i was quite puzzled as to what they could be. i then found an account of someone in palmyra ny who saw similar objects in the same area of the sky.
content.summary: About a dozen silvery white objects seen northeast of jamestown ny

content.detailedDescription: At approximately 9:20 pm on november 22, 2015 i was riding my bike home when i happened to look up at the sky. at first i thought it was a bat but upon further inspection it was an elongated black object traveling faster than an airplane and a very close to the ground traveling north to south. i made visual contact for about five seconds before the object turned south east and within a blink of an eye went left than straight up while leaving a white light trail behind only lasting a second. still thinking this was a bat, i was very confused. it took me a minute to process that this was definitely not an animal but a machine. there is no possible way this was an animal or a human machine because of the maneuvers it took and its  amount of power it generated in under a  second. the only reason i was able to see this object is because of the overwhelming light pollution coming off from the city and the almost full moon making the sky appear blue rather than black. if these conditions weren't exactly like they were, i would have not been able to see the black object.
content.summary: Very dark elongated vessel.

content.detailedDescription: My grandson his dog and i walkedto the beehive market to get a few things and walk the dog .We left my house 33 morton st yuba city . ca. at roughly 6 pm and arrived at the store at about 605 to 610 pm and grabbed. a few things then left we were about100 feet from the store when my grandson said look at the airplane papa i looked up and all i could see was lights that where like rectangular. in shape and about forty to fifty  feet acorss each set of lights of which. there were five sets of lights.  it almost. looked like the shape of.The number 5 as it appears on dice the lights that is but elongated the lights were very bright but not as bright as spot lights  and aimed straight down and flashing with no other lights anywhere i could see .The object was flying almost directly towards. sacramento. airport when i got. to the street that i live on. it was about. 1.5- 2.5miles past my street. as i walked down the street towards. my house. the object made  a slow right turn to the west southwest towards highway 99 and out of my line of sight .  then about five minutes later a helicopter blacked out except for a green light and a red light flew out of the south slowly to the north
content.summary: My grandson and i were walking home from the store when my grandson said look at the.Airplane. if this was a plane it was first one i ever saw with rectangular. lights in shape of number 5 on dice
